data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!! This home is eligible for SPECIAL FINANCING INCENTIVES!! Here's your chance to own a Denver home in Irving Park neighborhood. Location! Location! Location! Remodeled kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and white cabinetry. Bedrooms on opposite sides of the house with an updated bathroom in between. This home has 2 fenced in yards offering more than enough room to expand, R/V parking, or use your imagination! Fresh mulch and rock landscaping to help conserve water and save time. No HOA fees and low taxes! Come check out this move in ready home for yourself!!
